OL,3,CTeacher pay talks can proceed after
OL,4,Cministerial direction approved
OL,6,FDiscussions over a pay award for
OL,7,Fteachers in Northern Ireland can now
OL,8,Fprogress following approval for
OL,9,FEducation Minister Paul Givan to
OL,10,Foverspend his budget.
OL,12,FThe minister said he had used the
OL,13,Furgent decision procedure to get
OL,14,Fapproval for his ministerial direction
OL,15,Fto reflect the "importance of avoiding
OL,16,Ffurther delay in progressing teachers'
OL,17,Fpay arrangements".
OL,19,FMr Givan had previously been critical
OL,20,Fthat his direction was not accepted at
OL,21,Fan Executive meeting earlier this week.
