OL,6,F"Following yesterday's Executive
OL,7,Fmeeting, I wrote to the First Minister
OL,8,Fand the deputy First Minister setting
OL,9,Fout both the decision required and the
OL,10,Fimplications of deferring it.
OL,12,F"The First Minister and deputy First
OL,13,FMinister have now considered the
OL,14,Fmatter, and I am pleased that approval
OL,15,Fhas been given for the ministerial
OL,16,Fdirection.
OL,18,F"This enables discussions to progress
OL,19,Fand provides an important step towards
OL,20,Fensuring teachers are treated fairly."
