OL,6,FThe minister said the financial
OL,7,Fpressures on his department remain
OL,8,Facute.
OL,10,FMr Givan added: "I continue to work
OL,11,Fwith officials and the Education
OL,12,FAuthority to reduce the projected
OL,13,Fdeficit of circa #267m for this
OL,14,Ffinancial year, but critical pressures
OL,15,Fpersist.
OL,17,F"My decision to bring forward a
OL,18,Fdirection underlines my continued
OL,19,Fcommitment to Northern Ireland's
OL,20,Fteaching professionals and the pupils
OL,21,Fand school communities they serve."
