OL,6,FThe minister said the Teachers'
OL,7,FNegotiating Committee (TNC) would meet
OL,8,Fearly in the new year to take the pay
OL,9,Foffer forward.
OL,11,FThe Northern Ireland Teachers' Council
OL,12,F(NITC), representing the five main
OL,13,Fteacher unions, said it looked forward
OL,14,Fto engaging with the TNC over pay in
OL,15,FJanuary.
