OL,6,FA statement said: "Our focus remains
OL,7,Fon securing a fair and sustainable pay
OL,8,Foffer for teachers, who have waited
OL,9,Fpatiently for progress amidst the
OL,10,Fongoing pressures within the education
OL,11,Fsystem."
